---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="ChatGPT Optimisation Agency UK - Rank4AI" description="ChatGPT optimisation agency in the UK. We get your business recommended by ChatGPT through Bing ecosystem building, entity clarity and consistent digital presence.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Chatgpt Optimisation Agency' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">ChatGPT Optimisation</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">ChatGPT Optimisation Agency UK</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">ChatGPT has 900+ million weekly active users. When someone asks it to recommend a business in your category, it either mentions you or it does not. There is no page 2.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is a UK AI search agency that helps businesses get recommended by ChatGPT. We build the signals ChatGPT needs to confidently mention your business: Bing presence, entity clarity, independent citations, and consistent positioning across the web.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">How ChatGPT Optimisation Works</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">ChatGPT's primary web retrieval index is Bing. Building in the Microsoft and Bing ecosystem is the most direct ChatGPT visibility strategy available. We also build across Google, directories, review platforms and the wider web - because ChatGPT cross-references all of them.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">For the full guide, see <a href="/learn/guides/chatgpt-seo/" class="link">ChatGPT SEO - Complete UK Guide</a>.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">See how we compare: <a href="/research/rankings/best-chatgpt-seo-agencies-uk/" class="link">Best ChatGPT SEO Agencies UK 2026</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Services</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Complete AI Search Guide</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
